---
title: topkg porting
author: mirageos devs
abstract: status of topkg ported libraries
tags: active project, core, help needed
---

Topkg is [the transitory OCaml package builder](http://erratique.ch/software/topkg/doc/Topkg), well-designed and slicker than oasis.

It also enforces naming policies for metadata (LICENSE, README, CHANGES, etc), and nicely integrates documentation and metadata retrieval with [odig](http://erratique.ch/software/odig).

There are still some issues with C stubs, we wait for [ocb-stubblr](https://github.com/pqwy/ocb-stubblr) on that front.

## Libraries ported

- see [list](http://opam.ocaml.org/packages/topkg/)

## Libraries need porting

